flowchart TD
  req[Gateway receives request]
  call[Call upstream adapter]
  classify{Failure class}

  req --> call --> classify

  classify -->|network timeout| unavailable[Return 503 upstream_unavailable]
  classify -->|upstream 4xx| passthrough4xx[Passthrough status/body]
  classify -->|upstream 5xx| passthrough5xx[Passthrough status/body]
  classify -->|malformed upstream payload| protocolError[Return 502 or 500 gateway protocol error]

  unavailable --> obs[Emit logs/traces/metrics with correlation_id]
  passthrough4xx --> obs
  passthrough5xx --> obs
  protocolError --> obs

  obs --> done([Response completed])
